high_descs: Turn around and head to the coffee-maker on the right.
Pick up the cup from the coffee-maker.
Turn right and head to the microwave on the counter.
Put the cup in the microwave, heat it up, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn around and head to the coffee-maker on the counter on your right.
Put the cup in the coffee-maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a cup of coffee.

high_descs: go to the coffee maker on the counter
pick up the cup off of the coffee maker
turn around and walk over to the microwave
place the cup inside the microwave, microwave the cup, and then pick it up again
walk back over to the coffee maker
place the coffee cup underneath the spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: put a microwaved cup underneath the coffee maker spout

high_descs: Turn left, walk across the kitchen and then turn right so you are standing in front of the countertop.
Pick up the white mug that is under the coffee machine.
Turn right and carry the mug over to the microwave.
Open the microwave, heat the mug in it then remove it and close the microwave door again.
Turn around to the left and walk back over to the counter-top.
Place the mug back in to the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the mug from the coffee machine, heat it in the microwave before returning it to the coffee machine.
